
    COPS in Waterval outside Makhado in Limpopo have bust a 31-year-old parolee for murder and attempted murder.It is alleged the parolee had a domestic dispute with
his 25-year-old wife, which led to him stabbing her several times with a sharp
object."He further
stabbed their two children aged 5 and 3-years-old several times throughout
their bodies before fleeing the scene," Police Spokesperson Colonel
